{"tid":809523,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[cccu]求救!成個tutorial Class都係大陸狗","createTime":"2018-09-07T09:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T15:47:39.000Z","uid":160375,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e872b86a1f95de80aa88809aff9086c1bb0d2a","tid":809523,"uid":160375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:00:01.000Z","msg":"我讀cccu嘅<br />\n因為我係轉科,cccu office做野又閪又慢<br />\n所以去到8月31號先幫我鳩分tutorial班<br />\n(聽講第一班係外國學生,第二班係香港人,第三班係支那豬)<br />\n到oday嗰日 <br />\n我識咗我班tutorial個class rep(唯一香港人)<br />\n交換咗電話就自然入咗班whatsapp group<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">dllm</span></span><br />\n發現18條友10+條都係係大陸狗!<br />\n啲message全部都係&quot;啥,什麼&quot;<br />\n<br />\n到第一日上堂,一坐低,隔離條友就問我:<br />\n&quot;你會不會講普通話?&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母!</span><br />\n你落黎搶學位 搶樓住 搶奶粉 仲要我講你啲話?<br />\n但因為我係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我冇應佢就算<br />\n<br />\n依家 我去同programme leader講想轉tutorial班<br />\n佢話冇特別理由唔撚比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全能嘅連登仔 請打救我!<br />\n<br />\n唔想同支那豬一組<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4df3317105c9f519248d4f1d0cb03e3031b1895","tid":809523,"uid":160375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b1dadff9a44ad98bf88afb2e95bb16c12991ae8e","tid":809523,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:04:33.000Z","msg":"啥,什麼&quot; 草你媽逼"},{"pid":"64efa0cc70b108926a25744243f6667ad3000345","tid":809523,"uid":192491,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"起身, 大叫：<br />\nlz牛逼66666666666<br />\nskr, skr!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0c6e998e6693963658434facfb1d6c73047e2d","tid":809523,"uid":160375,"like":9,"disl